[
  {
    "text": "Hello, App Store developers. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=0"
  },
  {
    "text": "I'm Greg from the App Store Review team. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=1"
  },
  {
    "text": "Today I'm going to share tips from our team ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=4"
  },
  {
    "text": "to help you write clear, succinct purpose strings.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=6"
  },
  {
    "text": "At Apple, we believe that privacy ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=11"
  },
  {
    "text": "is a fundamental human right, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=12"
  },
  {
    "text": "and so Apple products are designed to protect privacy ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=14"
  },
  {
    "text": "and give users control over their information. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=17"
  },
  {
    "text": "In addition to designing our products ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=21"
  },
  {
    "text": "with privacy protections, privacy is central ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=22"
  },
  {
    "text": "in the App Store Review guidelines. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=25"
  },
  {
    "text": "Guideline 5.1.1, in particular, details some requirements ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=27"
  },
  {
    "text": "that are essential for protecting user privacy ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=31"
  },
  {
    "text": "in the Apple ecosystem, like minimizing the data ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=33"
  },
  {
    "text": "you collect to just what you need. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=36"
  },
  {
    "text": "Today we're going to focus on one requirement ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=40"
  },
  {
    "text": "we see both new and experienced developers struggle with: ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=42"
  },
  {
    "text": "being clear and transparent when requesting permission ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=46"
  },
  {
    "text": "to access protected resources. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=49"
  },
  {
    "text": "We'll share tips and examples to help you prevent ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=52"
  },
  {
    "text": "a common 5.1.1 rejection: insufficient purpose strings. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=54"
  },
  {
    "text": "We'll start by giving some background ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=60"
  },
  {
    "text": "on permission requests and the role they play ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=62"
  },
  {
    "text": "in protecting user privacy. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=64"
  },
  {
    "text": "We'll then focus in on purpose strings, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=67"
  },
  {
    "text": "short descriptions provided by you to describe why ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=69"
  },
  {
    "text": "your app needs access, and talk about some things ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=72"
  },
  {
    "text": "App Store Review looks for in review. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=75"
  },
  {
    "text": "We'll then finish with examples of purpose strings ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=78"
  },
  {
    "text": "that wouldn't pass review and discuss ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=81"
  },
  {
    "text": "how they can be rewritten to be clear and specific. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=82"
  },
  {
    "text": "But first, let's talk about permission requests. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=87"
  },
  {
    "text": "Our devices are an important part of our lives. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=91"
  },
  {
    "text": "What people share from their devices should be up to them, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=94"
  },
  {
    "text": "which is why all Apple operating systems ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=97"
  },
  {
    "text": "restrict access to protected data and resources by default.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=99"
  },
  {
    "text": "To access this information, apps must first request ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=105"
  },
  {
    "text": "the user's permission. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=108"
  },
  {
    "text": "This puts users in control -- ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=110"
  },
  {
    "text": "they can decide which apps have access to what. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=112"
  },
  {
    "text": "But to make an informed decision, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=115"
  },
  {
    "text": "people need to know more about why your app needs access ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=116"
  },
  {
    "text": "and what it will do once it has it. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=120"
  },
  {
    "text": "This is where purpose strings -- also called ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=123"
  },
  {
    "text": "\"usage descriptions,\" -- come in. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=124"
  },
  {
    "text": "A purpose string is a short message you provide ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=128"
  },
  {
    "text": "that appears on every permission request. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=130"
  },
  {
    "text": "It describes why your app needs access ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=133"
  },
  {
    "text": "and what you will do with the user's data. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=136"
  },
  {
    "text": "You'll define these messages on an app's ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=139"
  },
  {
    "text": "information property list -- or info p-list -- ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=141"
  },
  {
    "text": "by setting a string value to a resource-specific key. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=144"
  },
  {
    "text": "This is an important interaction between you and your app's users ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=148"
  },
  {
    "text": "on Apple operating systems. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=152"
  },
  {
    "text": "It's a chance to build trust by being clear and specific ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=154"
  },
  {
    "text": "about what your app is trying to do. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=157"
  },
  {
    "text": "Why is this so important? ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=159"
  },
  {
    "text": "Let's compare these permission requests from apps ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=161"
  },
  {
    "text": "with a situation from the real world; ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=164"
  },
  {
    "text": "one that you've probably experienced before. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=166"
  },
  {
    "text": "Imagine you go to buy a cup of coffee from a local coffee shop. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=169"
  },
  {
    "text": "Coffee in hand, you're ready to pay ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=173"
  },
  {
    "text": "when the cashier asks for your phone number. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=175"
  },
  {
    "text": "Huh. They haven't asked for that before, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=178"
  },
  {
    "text": "so why would they need it? ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=179"
  },
  {
    "text": "This can go one of two ways. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=181"
  },
  {
    "text": "The cashier could say, \"We use your number ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=183"
  },
  {
    "text": "to provide a better coffee-drinking experience.\" ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=186"
  },
  {
    "text": "So that sounds great, but it's not very specific ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=189"
  },
  {
    "text": "and it's not clear what that means. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=191"
  },
  {
    "text": "On the other hand, they could tell you ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=193"
  },
  {
    "text": "how they use your number to track your purchases, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=195"
  },
  {
    "text": "rewarding you with a free cup of coffee ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=197"
  },
  {
    "text": "for every fifth cup you buy. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=199"
  },
  {
    "text": "In both cases, it's up to you what happens next, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=201"
  },
  {
    "text": "only in the second example do you have the information ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=204"
  },
  {
    "text": "you need to make an informed decision. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=207"
  },
  {
    "text": "This kind of positive user experience ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=211"
  },
  {
    "text": "is what App Store Review looks for ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=212"
  },
  {
    "text": "when reviewing purpose strings. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=214"
  },
  {
    "text": "We make sure the purpose string gives users the information ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=217"
  },
  {
    "text": "they need to make an informed decision. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=220"
  },
  {
    "text": "What does this look like when we review your app? ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=223"
  },
  {
    "text": "Well, we approach apps like a new user would. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=226"
  },
  {
    "text": "This means we see permission request alerts ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=229"
  },
  {
    "text": "just as your users will when we try to use features ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=232"
  },
  {
    "text": "that access protected resources. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=235"
  },
  {
    "text": "This way we understand the full experience ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=238"
  },
  {
    "text": "and can anticipate what people need to know ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=241"
  },
  {
    "text": "to make informed decisions. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=243"
  },
  {
    "text": "So in review, we look for two key qualities ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=246"
  },
  {
    "text": "in purpose strings. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=249"
  },
  {
    "text": "They should explain specifically how the app will use the data ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=251"
  },
  {
    "text": "and provide an example of how the data will be used.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=256"
  },
  {
    "text": "Let's take a look at some examples ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=262"
  },
  {
    "text": "to see what purpose strings look like ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=263"
  },
  {
    "text": "when they have these two qualities ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=265"
  },
  {
    "text": "and what it's like for users when they don't. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=267"
  },
  {
    "text": "First, we have a navigation app ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=271"
  },
  {
    "text": "that specializes in recommending scenic routes. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=273"
  },
  {
    "text": "When users try to access the navigation feature, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=276"
  },
  {
    "text": "this is what they see: ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=278"
  },
  {
    "text": "\"To use location.\" ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=281"
  },
  {
    "text": "Not much to go on, right? ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=285"
  },
  {
    "text": "When you're developing an app, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=286"
  },
  {
    "text": "you know exactly what you will use a resource for. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=287"
  },
  {
    "text": "But users don't have the same understanding about ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=290"
  },
  {
    "text": "how your app works. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=293"
  },
  {
    "text": "They rely on the information you provide in the purpose string ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=295"
  },
  {
    "text": "to make their decision, and in this case, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=298"
  },
  {
    "text": "the user doesn't have the information they need. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=300"
  },
  {
    "text": "To build trust, this developer needs to say specifically ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=303"
  },
  {
    "text": "how they plan to use the data and provide an example. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=306"
  },
  {
    "text": "This would be better. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=311"
  },
  {
    "text": "\"Your location is used to determine the recommended route ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=312"
  },
  {
    "text": "to your destination and provide turn-by-turn directions.\" ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=314"
  },
  {
    "text": "Now the purpose string is specific ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=319"
  },
  {
    "text": "and provides concrete examples of what the app will be ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=320"
  },
  {
    "text": "able to do with the user's location data. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=323"
  },
  {
    "text": "Keep in mind, if your app supports localizations ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=327"
  },
  {
    "text": "for a global audience, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=329"
  },
  {
    "text": "be sure to provide localized purpose strings as well. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=331"
  },
  {
    "text": "We recommend testing your app set to different localizations ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=334"
  },
  {
    "text": "to confirm the user sees the correct localized app content. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=337"
  },
  {
    "text": "Well, let's take a look at another example. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=343"
  },
  {
    "text": "Here we have a social network app. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=345"
  },
  {
    "text": "The developer shares data collected in the app ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=347"
  },
  {
    "text": "with third parties to deliver targeted advertisements. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=350"
  },
  {
    "text": "Before collecting any data used to track though, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=354"
  },
  {
    "text": "they need to request permission using App Tracking Transparency. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=357"
  },
  {
    "text": "When you first open the app, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=361"
  },
  {
    "text": "the App Tracking Transparency permission request appears. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=363"
  },
  {
    "text": "Here's what it currently says: ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=367"
  },
  {
    "text": "\"Your data will be used to provide a better experience.\" ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=369"
  },
  {
    "text": "So this may be true, but it doesn't tell the user ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=374"
  },
  {
    "text": "what they need to know. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=376"
  },
  {
    "text": "How, specifically, will their data be used? ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=378"
  },
  {
    "text": "What's an example of the better experience ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=381"
  },
  {
    "text": "they should expect if they grant permission? ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=383"
  },
  {
    "text": "A better approach would be: ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=386"
  },
  {
    "text": "\"Your data will be used to deliver personalized advertising ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=389"
  },
  {
    "text": "for products that are most relevant to you.\" ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=392"
  },
  {
    "text": "Now it's clear what the developer will do ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=396"
  },
  {
    "text": "with this information and what the user would gain ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=397"
  },
  {
    "text": "from granting access. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=399"
  },
  {
    "text": "This developer could even provide more context ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=402"
  },
  {
    "text": "about what would happen if the user says no to tracking. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=404"
  },
  {
    "text": "\"Your data will be used ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=408"
  },
  {
    "text": "to deliver personalized advertising. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=409"
  },
  {
    "text": "You will still see advertisements ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=411"
  },
  {
    "text": "if you decline tracking, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=413"
  },
  {
    "text": "but they may be less relevant to you.\" ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=414"
  },
  {
    "text": "Either of these examples would be fitting for this app. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=418"
  },
  {
    "text": "The goal is to be transparent and clear ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=421"
  },
  {
    "text": "at the moment you request permission. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=423"
  },
  {
    "text": "Another thing to keep in mind; many apps on the App Store ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=426"
  },
  {
    "text": "integrate third-party SDKs and libraries. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=429"
  },
  {
    "text": "These SDKs and libraries can provide a wide variety ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=433"
  },
  {
    "text": "of features and services, such as account authentication. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=436"
  },
  {
    "text": "What you may not realize is they can also reference ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=440"
  },
  {
    "text": "APIs that will try to access protected resources, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=442"
  },
  {
    "text": "like location data. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=446"
  },
  {
    "text": "If your app has a reason to access these resources, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=447"
  },
  {
    "text": "define a purpose string on the info p-list ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=450"
  },
  {
    "text": "that applies to your app's specific use case. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=452"
  },
  {
    "text": "If not, you should remove references to these APIs ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=456"
  },
  {
    "text": "from your app's binary. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=458"
  },
  {
    "text": "Remember, you are responsible for everything in your app, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=461"
  },
  {
    "text": "including SDKs, libraries, or other code from third parties. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=464"
  },
  {
    "text": "When developing your app, be sure to familiarize yourself ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=469"
  },
  {
    "text": "with any protected resources they may try to access ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=471"
  },
  {
    "text": "and ensure that these requests are intentional ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=474"
  },
  {
    "text": "before submitting your app for review.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=476"
  },
  {
    "text": "So you might have noticed the examples so far ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=481"
  },
  {
    "text": "have focused on purpose strings with too little information. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=483"
  },
  {
    "text": "But what about the opposite? ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=486"
  },
  {
    "text": "Is there such a thing as too much information? ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=488"
  },
  {
    "text": "Let's see what this could look like. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=492"
  },
  {
    "text": "Here we have an app for local gardeners ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=494"
  },
  {
    "text": "where you can look at pictures of your friends' gardens. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=496"
  },
  {
    "text": "When we go to take our first picture, however, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=499"
  },
  {
    "text": "we see the developer chose to include a long description ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=501"
  },
  {
    "text": "on the request. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=503"
  },
  {
    "text": "Let me see if I can do this in one breath. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=505"
  },
  {
    "text": " ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=507"
  },
  {
    "text": "\"Whether you're just discovering your green thumb ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=508"
  },
  {
    "text": "or a veteran plant expert, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=509"
  },
  {
    "text": "use our app to share your love of gardening! ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=510"
  },
  {
    "text": "With access to your camera, you'll be able to take ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=512"
  },
  {
    "text": "profile pictures posing with your favorite succulent, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=513"
  },
  {
    "text": "capture your raised beds in their best afternoon light, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=515"
  },
  {
    "text": "and much, much more!\" ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=517"
  },
  {
    "text": "A bit much, isn't it? ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=520"
  },
  {
    "text": "Usually just a sentence or two is enough ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=521"
  },
  {
    "text": "to tell people what they need to know. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=523"
  },
  {
    "text": "For our garden app, this would be better: ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=525"
  },
  {
    "text": "\"Our app uses the camera to capture photos ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=529"
  },
  {
    "text": "for updating and sharing on your gardener profile.\" ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=531"
  },
  {
    "text": "Now the purpose string is specific and includes examples ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=535"
  },
  {
    "text": "that cover the various uses of the camera in the app. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=537"
  },
  {
    "text": "Not too long, not too short, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=542"
  },
  {
    "text": "purpose strings should be just right. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=544"
  },
  {
    "text": "Longer, wordier purpose strings ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=546"
  },
  {
    "text": "can be accurate and may pass review, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=548"
  },
  {
    "text": "but they're not the ideal experience for the user. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=551"
  },
  {
    "text": "Keep the description straightforward and to the point ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=554"
  },
  {
    "text": "so it's easy to read and understand ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=556"
  },
  {
    "text": "when viewed in the app. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=558"
  },
  {
    "text": "Let's put all of that together ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=561"
  },
  {
    "text": "and go on a quick permission request journey ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=562"
  },
  {
    "text": "with one of our hypothetical apps. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=565"
  },
  {
    "text": "Accurately and concisely explaining to the user ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=568"
  },
  {
    "text": "why your app needs access to sensitive data lets the user ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=571"
  },
  {
    "text": "make an informed decision and improves the chances ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=574"
  },
  {
    "text": "that they'll grant access, so that your app ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=577"
  },
  {
    "text": "will function for them exactly as you've intended. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=579"
  },
  {
    "text": "It allows you to describe your app's unique experience ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=584"
  },
  {
    "text": "while keeping the user in control ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=587"
  },
  {
    "text": "of their personal information. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=589"
  },
  {
    "text": "And understanding that users will make their decision ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=592"
  },
  {
    "text": "to grant access based on what you write will help you ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=594"
  },
  {
    "text": "add the appropriate context to your purpose strings ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=597"
  },
  {
    "text": "to keep them relevant, transparent, and informative.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=599"
  },
  {
    "text": "Keep these examples in mind for your future submissions ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=607"
  },
  {
    "text": "to the App Store. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=609"
  },
  {
    "text": "We hope they help you keep users informed and allow them ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=611"
  },
  {
    "text": "to enjoy everything your app has to offer. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=613"
  },
  {
    "text": "Thanks for watching our video. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=618"
  },
  {
    "text": "To learn more about permission requests ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=620"
  },
  {
    "text": "and developing with privacy in mind, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=621"
  },
  {
    "text": "there's helpful guides and documentation ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=623"
  },
  {
    "text": "on the Apple Developer website ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=625"
  },
  {
    "text": "and in the Human Interface Guidelines. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=626"
  },
  {
    "text": "We look forward to reviewing your future submissions ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=629"
  },
  {
    "text": "to the App Store.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110152/?time=631"
  }
]